[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/thief">Thief</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/thief">Thief</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user attacks and steals the foe's held item simultaneously. It can't steal if the user holds an item.</p>